    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Huge and dangerous bugs are attacking you. Grow mutated plants that can shoot and defend themselves. <span class=\"bb_strike\">Build</span> Grow a reliable defense so that the bugs cannot break the core.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/426fd4453b0acf2082d6ecd6bdb3c071.poster.avif?t=1756210485\" width=734 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/426fd4453b0acf2082d6ecd6bdb3c071.webm?t=1756210485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/426fd4453b0acf2082d6ecd6bdb3c071.mp4?t=1756210485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay loop of the game looks like this:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant seeds in the soil so that crops can grow from them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Grow</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of plants during the day and support the balance of nutrients in the ecosystem.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutate</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select several plants and apply the secret growth formula on them.<br>They will mutate into “towers” ​​and will be able to protect you and the entire base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At night you are attacked by bugs and your tower-plants fire at them.  <br>You too can join in the battle with your own pistol to save the situation, but be careful...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How long will you last?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable enemy path.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bugs do not follow prepared paths. <br>Everyone has their own AI and they constantly analyze the situation and choose to move in a certain direction. <br>Ultimately, all bugs move towards the player or towards the core, but there are baits. <br>With their help, you can direct enemies in some direction or lure them into deadly zones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Spices&quot; for towers.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow new types of plants which can be made into spices.<br>Apply them to towers and receive an upgrade.<br>Additional damage or an enemy health filter...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/b1ac33c4637efc4e6769a86cbb5bedfd.poster.avif?t=1756210485\" width=780 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/b1ac33c4637efc4e6769a86cbb5bedfd.webm?t=1756210485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244360/extras/b1ac33c4637efc4e6769a86cbb5bedfd.mp4?t=1756210485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Well-developed nutrient mechanics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simply planting the seeds and waiting is not enough for growing good plants. <br>The game has a nutrient exchange system.<br>For example, potatoes secrete the nutrient &quot;Potatium&quot;, which in large quantities slows down the growth of potatoes. <br>Thus, after some time, they will need to be moved to another soil or other vegetables planted in order to restore the nutrient balance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Defense + Farming</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a unique combination of Tower Defense and Farming genres. <br>During the day you tend to your garden.<br>Plant seeds, grow plants and care for them.<br>At night, bugs attack and the game turns into Tower Defense. <br>Mutated plants act as “towers” ​​and protect you from enemies.</p>",
